    <abstract>
      <t>The current RPKI Resource Certificate Repository Structure (RFC6480 &amp; RFC6481) uses rsync as both a delta and transfer protocol. Concerns have been raised about the scalability of this repository and the reliance on rsync. This document provides an analysis of these concerns and formulates requirements for future work.</t>
